{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4e85a7b368","title":"改哥老会为江湖抗口救国会","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8a64cbf5b8","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"4e85a7b368"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a32101e27d","type":"paragraph","text":"改哥老会为江湖抗口救国会","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4e85a7b368"},{"id":"f0cfb3e608","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月19日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4e85a7b368"},{"id":"97eed67680","type":"paragraph","text":"我们对哥老会以统一战线的策略争取其大多数到抗日战线上来；不应勉强使回人哥老会加入汉人哥老会，也不应勉强将他们合并，必须坚持回人事情由回人自己处理的原则","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4e85a7b368"},{"id":"f345bac45c","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和杨尚昆关于改哥老会为江湖抗日救国会问题致红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀，政治部主任刘晓电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4e85a7b368"}],"page":{"id":"e5cddde010","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"4e85a7b368","start":78,"end":78}}}},"__N_SSG":true}